name: OUT WITH [THE] OLD
description:
To celebrate #HEN500K, we're finishing a chapter in the creative process that has been a journey with GAN. AI-Generated art has been a fun and enjoyable experience to work with, but it's time to start the next chapter. 

"Out With The Old" is a quadriptych to usher in the next phase of digitalgyoza x H=N 

Collect all four to have the full phrase. 
However, they are also 1/1 editions.

First Come, First Served.
